Project.Title: HighClass
Project.Summary: An educational web platform designed to assist students in balancing their studies, tests, and workload. With features like personalized study schedules and resource recommendations, HighClass aims to enhance students' learning experiences and academic performance.

Project.Title: Xyrox AI

Project.Title: Referral Code Generator
